# Filament Panels

Three panels, all extending `CommonPanelProvider`:

| Panel | Provider | Path | Purpose |
|-------|----------|------|---------|
| App | `AppPanelProvider` | `/` | Member site: tickets, volunteer, grants, account |
| Admin | `AdminPanelProvider` | `/admin` | Staff CRUD, sales charts, event management |
| Gate | `GatePanelProvider` | `/gate` | Offline gate check-in, QR scanning |

Auto-discovery paths: `app/Filament/{Admin|App|Gate}/{Resources|Pages|Widgets|Clusters}`.

## Conventions

- Auth guard is `web` (session), not JWT
- Gate visibility and field access use `Auth::user()->can('permission.name')`
- Admin resources are event-scoped via `Event::getCurrentEvent()` — hide nav with `shouldRegisterNavigation()`
- Add `AuditsRelationManager` on resources for auditable models
- Volunteering uses **Guava nested resources**: `TeamResource` → `ShiftTypeResource` → `ShiftResource`
- Custom `FarAncestor` in `app/Filament/NestedResources/` for `HasManyThrough` nesting
- Imports/exports in `app/Filament/Imports/` and `Exports/`
- Custom form components in `app/Forms/Components/`
- App panel uses **clusters** for user account pages (`UserPages` cluster)
- Shared auth pages in `app/Filament/Pages/Auth/`

## Adding Admin Resources

Match existing resources: permission-gated fields, event scoping where relevant, relation managers for audits, nested pages for child resources (see `TeamResource` for the volunteering pattern).
